{
  "stem": "17.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 269.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So the day came, we loaded whatever possible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because whatever we-- our belongings.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So that was the only thing that we could carry on us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was November 26, '92.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And that was strong, severe winter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We were not used to walking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And in the morning, that was this march from the ghetto to the, to the Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was terribly slippery.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We were loaded, not used to, to this weight, carrying the weight and also to, to walk.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But the people were helping us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And somehow, I don't know how, how was it possibly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It was a deadly march, physically.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We arrived to this factory.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And Henry put us in the spot behind the wall, behind the boxes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we were supposed to wait for the evening.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We never knew if he will make it, if we will make it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "It was freezing cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we were trying to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] talk to each other, encourage each other.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Finally, it was 6 o'clock in the evening, dark.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Here he came, you know, embrace us and said, here we are going to a new life.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And he engaged-- that was a carriage with the horses.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And he said, here are our new names, new identities.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We tore up completely whatever we have-- our old papers, our old names, photographs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I don't have my father's picture.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We tore up everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And we are going-- we are going to a new, new life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And we got one good advice, which was good for the rest of the life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Don't ask any question and don't be surprised.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Because that's, that's how you can-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I mean, you can blame yourself for, for, for making a mistake.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
